      <title>监管机构警告称，特朗普计划将削减社会保障福利 33%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/trump-s-plans-set-social-security-benefits-up-for-33-cut-watchdog-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个无党派预算监督组织周一估计，唐纳德·特朗普的第二总统任期议程将导致社会保障体系提前三年破产，并最终导致福利削减近三分之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/trump-s-plans-set-social-security-benefits-up-for-33-cut-watchdog-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 15:29:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
